        <!-- Time -->

        <!-- Status -->

        <!-- Permissions -->

      <div data-z-index-level="dialog-overlay" id="dialog-overlay" style="height: 460px;">
        <!-- Unlock SIM Pin dialog -->
        <div hidden="" data-z-index-level="simpin-dialog" role="dialog" id="simpin-dialog">
          <section role="region">
            <header>
              <button type="reset">
                <span class="icon icon-close" data-l10n-id="close">Close</span>
              </button>
              <menu type="toolbar">
                <button type="submit" data-l10n-id="ok">OK</button>
              </menu>
              <h1></h1>
            </header>

            <div class="container">
              <div hidden="" class="error" id="errorMsg">
                <div id="messageHeader">The PIN was incorrect.</div>
                <span id="messageBody">3 tries left.</span>
              </div>

              <!-- sim pin input field -->
              <div hidden="" id="pinArea">
                <div data-l10n-id="simPin">SIM PIN</div>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                  <input type="number" maxlength="8" size="8" name="simpin" />
                  <input type="text" maxlength="8" size="8" name="simpinVis" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- sim puk input field -->
              <div hidden="" id="pukArea">
                <div data-l10n-id="pukCode">PUK code</div>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                  <input type="number" maxlength="8" size="8" name="simpuk" />
                  <input type="text" maxlength="8" size="8" name="simpukVis" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- sim nck input field -->
              <div hidden="" id="nckArea">
                <div data-l10n-id="nckCode">NCK code</div>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                  <input type="number" maxlength="16" size="16" name="nckpin" />
                  <input type="text" maxlength="16" size="16" name="nckpinVis" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- new sim pin input field -->
              <div hidden="" id="newPinArea">
                <div data-l10n-id="newSimPinMsg">Create PIN (must contain 4 to 8 digits)</div>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                  <input type="number" maxlength="8" size="8" name="newSimpin" />
                  <input type="text" maxlength="8" size="8" name="newSimpinVis" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- confirm new sim pin input field -->
              <div hidden="" id="confirmPinArea">
                <div>Confirm New PIN</div>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                  <input type="number" maxlength="8" size="8" name="confirmNewSimpin" />
                  <input type="text" maxlength="8" size="8" name="confirmNewSimpinVis" />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <!-- Crash reporter -->
        <div id="crash-dialog">
          <form data-type="confirm" role="dialog">
            <section id="crash-dialog-contents">
              <h1 id="crash-dialog-title"></h1>
              <p data-l10n-id="crash-dialog-message">Would you like to send Mozilla a report about the crash to help us fix the problem? (Reports are sent over Wi-Fi only.)</p>
              <p><a data-l10n-id="crash-info-link" id="crash-info-link">What's in a crash report?</a></p>
              <p>
                <input type="checkbox" checked="true" id="always-send" />
                <label data-l10n-id="crash-always-report" for="always-send">Always send Mozilla a report when a crash occurs.</label>
              </p><p>
            </p></section>
            <menu>
              <button data-l10n-id="crash-dont-send" disabled="true" id="dont-send-report">Don't Send</button>
              <button data-l10n-id="crash-end" class="recommend" id="send-report">Send Report</button>
            </menu>
          </form>

          <!-- "Crash Reports" information page -->
          <section class="skin-dark" role="region">
            <header>
              <menu type="toolbar">
                <button data-l10n-id="done" id="crash-reports-done">Done</button>
              </menu>
              <h1 data-l10n-id="crashReports">Crash Reports</h1>
            </header>
            <p data-l10n-id="crash-reports-description-1">A crash report contains some details about the crash and your device, as well as a snapshot of the state of your device when it crashed.</p>
            <p data-l10n-id="crash-reports-description-2">This may include things like open pages and apps, text typed into forms and the content of open messages, recent browsing history, or geolocation used by an open app.</p>
            <p>
              <span data-l10n-id="crash-reports-description-3-start">We use crash reports to try to fix problems and improve our products. We handle your information as we describe in our </span><span data-l10n-id="crash-reports-description-3-privacy">privacy policy</span><span data-l10n-id="crash-reports-description-3-end">.</span>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div id="popup-container">
